
bin:
   kleinian:  complete compiled program on a Pentium-4. Chances are,
       you'll need to recompile.
   runklein: A script for running kleinian on a lot of script files.
       Say
           runklein *.dat

Indra:
   All the scripts used in the prpeartion of Indra's Pearls and more.
   Say
        kleinian < script.dat
   to run a script.

src:
   Source code. Edit the Makefile, then say
        make kleinian
        make install
   to install it.

Good luck!
